:{{A|VO chapter3 25 player 102 m.ogg}} {{A|VO chapter3 25 player 102 f.ogg}} '''(Trailblazer):''' (It's... Robin?)
:{{A|VO chapter3 25 blackswan 145.ogg}} '''Black Swan:''' Alright, please come with me.
:{{A|VO chapter3 25 player 101 m.ogg}} {{A|VO chapter3 25 player 101 f.ogg}} '''(Trailblazer):''' These people are...?
:{{A|VO chapter3 25 acheron 114.ogg}} '''Acheron:''' They're the ones who accept Ena's Dream and indulge in their happy illusions...
:{{A|VO chapter3 25 acheron 115.ogg}} '''Acheron:''' We have no means to wake them up now. Not even your clockwork will do the trick.
:{{A|VO chapter3 25 acheron 116.ogg}} '''Acheron:''' However, there are still other things we can do. Let's keep going.
